---
description: Enforce Cursor skill location and SKILL.md format compatibility
globs: .cursor/rules/**/*.mdc,.cursor/skills/**/SKILL.md,AGENTS.md
alwaysApply: false
---

# Skills Location and Format Rule

- Project skills must live in:
  - `.cursor/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md`
- `name` in SKILL frontmatter must match the parent folder name exactly.
- `SKILL.md` must include:
  - `When to Use`
  - `Instructions`
- Keep description explicit about what and when.
- Keep skill docs concise and reference project documents by path.
- If root `AGENTS.md` exists, keep it concise and non-duplicative; detailed task contracts belong in `.cursor/skills/` or `.cursor/rules/`.
